body_html:
We intentionally did not build 1.4.1 windows binaries, as the 1.4.1 only includes a fix for GCS and CloudML.
Our windows builds would have delayed the release, and we do not even include the GCS support on windows binaries anyway.
Is there a reason why you needed the 1.4.1 binary on windows?
